                  "inline_data": null,
                  "text": "Namaste! Welcome to SecureLife Insurance. Getting a proper auto insurance policy is a very smart move for your vehicle's *Suraksha* (protection). \n\nSince you are looking for a new quote, let me explain the simple process to get you the most *Paisa Vasool* (value-for-money) deal!\n\nFirst, to give you an accurate and customized quote, I just need a few basic details from your end:\n1. **Your Good Name** (so I can address you properly!)\n2. **Your Exact City** in Maharashtra (e.g., Mumbai, Pune, Nagpur, as this helps us check the local cashless garage network)\n3. **Vehicle Details**: The make, model, and manufacturing year of your car.\n\n**My \"Bada Bhai\" (Elder Brother) Advice to you:** Whenever buying auto insurance, always pay attention to the IDV (Insured Declared Value) and ensure your insurer has a strong network of cashless garages near your home. It’s not just about finding the lowest premium; it’s about a completely stress-free experience if you ever need to file a claim!\n\nPlease share these quick details with me, and I will immediately calculate the best premiums and discounts for you. Let's get started!",
